title: Classic games collection formatted for Mac OS X (Vol. 3)
description:
------------------
Vol. 3
------------------

Classic dos games formatted to run on OS X using a a modified version of Dosbox. Each game consists of one app file. Just click and run. Dosbox is universal binary.

Thanks to user fak-it for the special version of Dosbox.
